rez/glu*.bin:

86 bytes per entry.

offset  type     value
0	DWORD	 "next offset"?
4	WORD	 X1
6	WORD	 Y1
8	WORD	 X2
10	WORD	 Y2
12	WORD	 width
14	WORD	 height

20	DWORD	 text offset

24      DWORD    flags

28-34   ??

34      BYTE     type*


flags:

???               = 0x00000001
???               = 0x00000002
???               = 0x00000004
Visible           = 0x00000008
DisplayForControl = 0x00000010
???               = 0x00000020
CancelButton      = 0x00000040
???               = 0x00000080
???               = 0x00000100
HasHotkey         = 0x00000200
SmallerFont       = 0x00000400
LargerFont        = 0x00000800
???               = 0x00001000
AlignUnderImage   = 0x00002000
LargestFont       = 0x00004000
???               = 0x00008000
???               = 0x00010000
???               = 0x00020000
Image             = 0x00040000
DefaultButton     = 0x00080000
???               = 0x00100000
GreenText         = 0x00200000
???               = 0x00400000
???               = 0x00800000
???               = 0x01000000
???               = 0x02000000
???               = 0x04000000
???               = 0x08000000

types:
00 - Dialog Box
01 - Default Button
02 - Button
03 - Option Button
04 - Check Box
05 - Image
06 - Slider
08 - Text Box
09 - Label (Left align)
10 - Label (center align)
11 - Label (right align)
12 - List Box
13 - Combo Box
14 - Button without border


strings can have embedded 0x04/0x01.  0x04 seems to be "bold", 0x01 is
"normal", or maybe a different color in the colormap.  at any rate, it
is used to accentuate out the accelerator.
